    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, reduce the heat to medium-low</p><p>Add the <strong>bay leaves</strong>, <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>garlic</strong>, <strong>soy sauce</strong> and 4 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[8 tbsp] </span><strong>water</strong> and cook, covered, for 4-5 min or until the sauce has reduced slightly</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
