    {
      "instruction": "<p>Rinse the <strong>white long grain rice</strong> until the water runs clear, then add it to a pot with a lid with 225ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[450ml] </span><strong>cold water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>When the rice is boiling, add the <strong>Tenderstem broccoli</strong> and <strong>halved green beans</strong> and reduce the heat to very low and cook, covered, for 12-15 min or until all the water has absorbed and the rice is cooked</p><p>Once cooked, remove from the heat and keep covered until serving – this is your <strong>veggie rice</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
